data.description: PRICE DROP! PRICED TO SELL!! Step into the welcoming embrace of the "Trenton Model" home, a generously spacious two-story residence covering 3,327 sq ft. Boasting six bedrooms and three baths, this home is meticulously designed to cater to the discerning homeowner. The first floor not only houses the master suite but also offers the potential for an in-law suite, providing added convenience and flexibility.  Experience the practical elegance of a versatile flex room downstairs and a sprawling loft upstairs, tailored to accommodate your unique lifestyle. The kitchen, the heart of the home, showcases designer laminate countertops and 36” cabinets, creating a stylish and functional space for your daily activities. Indulge in the comfort of low-maintenance ceramic tile floors in key areas, and relish the modern conveniences provided by a programmable thermostat and a 40-gallon electric water heater. Situated in the SouthShore community, this home comes with a range of amenities including a playground, pool, clubhouse, scenic trails, and workout areas. Additionally, the proximity to EG Simmons Park and Little Manatee River State Park ensures outdoor enjoyment. From beaches to boating, golf to shopping, all the desired amenities are within easy reach. Don't let this opportunity pass by—schedule your showing today and step into the perfect retreat!
